未发现本轮阻塞性 finding。

N001 判定：`resolved-correct`。修复点在 [src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/exam_items_service.py:61](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/exam_items_service.py#L61) 和 [src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/exam_items_service.py:67](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/exam_items_service.py#L67)，现在先用 `q_matrix` 对 `assessment_items` 做 `INNER JOIN`，再计算 `item_ids/total` 并分页，所以 phantom id 会在分页前被过滤，`total / page_ids / items` 口径一致。防御性 `row is None` 分支还保留在 [src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/exam_items_service.py:101](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/src/edu_cloud/modules/knowledge_tree/exam_items_service.py#L101)，但按当前查询路径理论上不会再命中。

新增测试充分，`test_get_exam_items_total_consistent_with_actual_items` 位于 [tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_exam_items_service.py:140](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_exam_items_service.py#L140)，同时检查第一页 `total==2`、第二页空结果但 `total` 仍为 2、以及 `page_size=2` 时第一页装满两题，关键断言在 [tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_exam_items_service.py:180](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_exam_items_service.py#L180)、[tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_exam_items_service.py:186](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_exam_items_service.py#L186)、[tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_exam_items_service.py:192](/C:/Users/Administrator/edu-cloud/tests/test_knowledge_tree/test_exam_items_service.py#L192)。我在临时 worktree 中删除 `INNER JOIN` 后复跑该测试，实际失败并报出 `total=3`，说明它能有效杀掉“删掉 INNER JOIN”的 mutant。当前相关回归测试本地通过：`5 passed, 5 deselected`。

边界路径未见新 bug。当前实现对“无关联 DA”仍会早退为 `{total: 0, items: []}`；我额外做了“全部都是 phantom id、`assessment_items` 无任何对应行”的脚本验证，返回也是 `{'total': 0, 'items': [], 'page': 1, 'page_size': 10}`，说明 `INNER JOIN` 没把空集合/无关联路径弄坏。

结论：PASS。无新增 HIGH/MED `code-bug` 或 `test-gap`。
